0.0.1:
- support for more profiles (more MUC, settings)
- methods muc, msg, nick and bot are available in plugins directly
- Ctrl-c 1x => reload (plugins and core), 2x => terminate
- support for profiles (more MUCs, configurable format of message for command matching)
- can handle PM messages (send just command and its args, e. g. "about news")
- can handle resources

0.0.2:
- support for data storage by DataMapper
